    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 查看文件inode号</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">ls -i filename
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 输出: 131074 filename</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 查看inode详细信息</span>
